      "span_text": "This cell filter, along with several other ways to eliminate cells with unsuitable size or volume features, follows corresponding features of the Celltrack software  for 2D cell tracking; for ct3d, they are implemented in the graphical user interface of the at3d tool shown in Figure 4."
